[div class=p 
	"This strat was first developed by Matt Turk in 2004.  Start by jabbing to force him to counter jab then late punch for a star.  Do this 3 times, then unload 2 uppercuts immediately.  Then force another jab and late punch for a star.  Pause briefly and then throw a jab that will intercept Tiger while his ruby is flashing.  Now wait about 3 seconds and deliver an uppercut to intercept his next ruby flash which will knock him down.  On Phase 2 & 3 he will get up on 1 so just uppercut him immediately.
	$LF
