[h4 id=TurbanTantrum 
	" The Turban Tantrum
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Fastest time: 48.82
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Phase 1
	]b
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Start off by waiting until right before his jewel flashes then punch his face, he will block then punch back at you. Dodge his jab and do a very late punch to the face for a star, then right (Very quickly) after that punch his face again for star #2 while his jewel is flashing. Use the two stars and pause for just a split second then punch his face again and hopefully you will hit him while his jewel is flashing for another star, USE IT! Now wait until right before his jewel flashes again and punch, dodge and late punch his face for star #4, then right (very quickly again) after that punch his face for your last star. Now punch, he will block and do a late punch to knock him down! I knocked him down at about 0:42 or so.
	$LF
]div
